data.description: This spacious single-level split floorplan home includes 3 Beds, Teen Space, Study & 3.5 Baths. Oversized North/South lot w/10' gate, pavers drive, walk, entry, and private courtyard. Amazing Kitchen Features 42'' upper kitchen cabinets, dreamy enhanced kitchen island, Gas cooking with double oven, and a 30'' cooktop. Huge walk-in shower at owner's bath with ceramic tile surrounds, Linen (off-white), upgraded flooring includes 12x24 ceramic tile in all the right areas. 16-seer rated A/C unit, and so much more. Amazing Community Pool and amenities, Only a few minutes to Queen Creek's Agritourism District, Movie Theater, Shopping, Dining, and much more! Attention VA Buyers! Assumable 2.75% Mortgage for VA Buyers! Must Qualify!
